                            <comment id="17458881" author="emilles" created="Tue, 14 Dec 2021 03:44:56 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/apache/groovy/commit/e71a44a04eda3a0b27de7f54b2176c1e3fdafad1&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://github.com/apache/groovy/commit/e71a44a04eda3a0b27de7f54b2176c1e3fdafad1&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="17459424" author="emilles" created="Tue, 14 Dec 2021 19:15:51 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;The dynamic case runs through &lt;tt&gt;Outer$Inner#propertyMissing&lt;/tt&gt; which delegates to &lt;tt&gt;Outer#this$dist$get$1&lt;/tt&gt;.  It does not appear to distinguish between a call site that is within Outer and one that lies outside.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
